Class FileEventListener

java.lang.Object
  de.cau.cs.kieler.sim.kiem.config.extension.FileEventListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
IKiemEventListener
public class FileEventListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements IKiemEventListener

Listens to all events from the main KIEM Plugin and handles file related events.

Author:
soh

Field Summary
private static FileEventListener instance
          The last created instance of the event listener.

Used to set the load/save imminent variables.
This is done to prevent the listener from reporting
events that were triggered by the plugin itself.
private  boolean loadImminent
          A plugin-triggered load is imminent, don't handle.
private  boolean saveImminent
          A plugin-triggered save is imminent, don't handle.
